What you do as a Manager Institutional Clients Europe
Your mission is to lead the business unit, which services professional clients, to ensure that its full potential is reached. You will centralize the business activities through Europe to one aligned team and proposition and expand our services to different client types.
You will be responsible for:
Restructuring the business unit to a more efficient and centralized setup;
Expanding market share on servicing AIF funds;
Launching product/services to independent asset managers;
Creating a proposition to proprietary trading firms;
Expanding the business unit to new jurisdictions (e.g. Luxembourg);
