Your team consists out of approximately 10 employees across the Netherlands, Belgium, Germany, and the Czech Republic. The current client base contains mainly AIF funds. The focus is being expanded, however to independent asset managers and proprietary trading firms as well.
The management of LYNX sees great potential in serving professional clients and the plan for the coming years is to increase recourses to further expand the business unit. In addition, the goal is to restructure the international setup by centralizing the business unit to the Netherlands and using existing team members in other countries as local salespeople.
