You are good at actively expanding your network and in exploring opportunities for corporations or partnerships that could improve the position of LYNX;
You establish and maintains long-term relationships with top customers;
You are excellent in creating new concepts for services and products that have not been marketed before;
You see chances and opportunities for the organization before others do and acts accordingly;
You have the ability to provide guidance to the team and encourage cooperation between the team members in order to attain the team objectives; and
You discuss strategic goals, mission, and vision with the team members to inspire them to contribute to the overall objectives and ambitions.
