We’re looking for a Senior Talent Acquisition Specialist with Games recruiting experience!

Alderson James are working with a multi award-winning games studio with a catalog of awesome titles, as they look to bring in an experienced Games recruiter to their Talent & People team. You’ll work in a highly dynamic studio collaborating closely with the Senior team as you recruit across Level Design, VFX, Arts and Animations, Programming and Production.

Excellent package available, with relocation assistance provided if needed, considerable bonus and excellent benefits!

Responsibilities include…

Full cycle recruitment of Games positions at various levels;
Working with hiring managers to identify talent gaps, developing compelling job postings;
Sourcing passive, high-quality, games industry-specialist candidates through modern recruitment channels such as active sourcing, social media, network building, targeted advertising and advanced Boolean logic applications;
Interviewing and screening candidates to determine skill sets and cultural fit;
Researching and developing innovative strategies to recruit top talent;
Constantly seeking to raise the bar, identifying and proactively improving processes and candidate experience;
Regularly analysing and advising on pipeline and performance data to share with internal stakeholders;
