Are you looking for a diverse and challenging job in logistics, in a company where your personal initiatives will be noticed and highly valued? Do you want to develop yourself in a fast moving and result oriented environment? Join the Canon Logistics team located either in Maasvlakte, Rotterdam or Amstelveen.
The Logistics Specialist makes sure that logistics processes and policies in the EMEA region are correctly followed up with a key focus on driving continues improvement towards an effective, efficient and integrated logistics operation.
What we give
With Canon, you'll get the support and encouragement you need to grow, from people who share your ambition. We'll invest in your professional development to help you learn and progress in your role with us. You'll find leaders who give you the freedom to explore new things and a team where knowledge is shared openly.
In this exciting role you will:
Operate in an international, multifaceted environment to continuously seek opportunities to reduce logistic & warehousing costs and increase efficiency;
Coordinate and manage performance of multiple third-party service providers including 20+ key carriers and warehouse suppliers;
Independently plan and monitor transport in line with business requirements/agreements;
Monitor agreed logistic & warehousing KPIs & Service Level Agreements. Propose & implement corrective actions where required;
